commitResults.messageBody:
CreateDeadlineCommand is suppose to:
- create deadlines for all students in group if user specifies "allStu"
and is in a group directory.
- create deadlines for all groups in root if user specifies "allGrp"
and is in a root directory.

Currently, there are errors in the if else loop in CreateDeadlineCommand
class which leads to errors in CreateDeadlineCommandTest. Testcase for
CreateDeadlineCommandParser also have errors.
